        <num>CC 2812</num>
        <heading>2812.  The sharing of a partner's interest with a third person</heading>
        <content>
          <p>Art. 2812.  The sharing of a partner's interest with a third person.
A partner may share his interest in the partnership with a third person without the consent of his partners, but he cannot make him a member of the partnership.  He is responsible for damage to the partnership caused by the third person as though he caused it himself.</p>
        </content>
        <authorialNote marker="source">
